article_title: Six weeks of war between Hamas in Gaza and Israel.
sentence: The  Hamas-run  health  ministry  in  Gaza  says  more  than  12,000  people  have  been  killed  since  Israel  began  its  campaign  against  Hamas,  following  Hamas's  October  attack  on  Israel  that  killed  more  1,200  people.
